  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out whether a single fecal microbiota transplantation is
      an effective and safe treatment as an adjunct to standard therapy in patients with ulcerative
      colitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
